{"tid":2457171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU全新主打歌《Coin》預告玩味公開，最後壞笑的特寫鏡頭太帥氣啦～！","createTime":"2021-03-22T12:09:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T14:06:40.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f19ff5dc9feb2633a0f63486055f0cdcd174ec38","tid":2457171,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:09:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_9009d72acacadef5c03c69518095245f/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-22/134409-900850.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_9009d72acacadef5c03c69518095245f%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-22%2F134409-900850.jpg&h=c6317b47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這次 IU 的回歸風格真的太多變了，已有 4 部新歌預告，都各有新的驚喜跟看點。<br />\n<br />\n頂級 solo 女歌手 IU 即將在本週四（3月25日）正式回歸，官方今日又再度公開了一部新歌 MV，是 IU 此次雙主打曲《Coin》的預告。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_88d14c57839c8d7de3c684df8fa14836/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-22/134409-900851.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_88d14c57839c8d7de3c684df8fa14836%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-22%2F134409-900851.jpg&h=731230d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_cac30bb317eb79a24a6b408d60ea662e/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-22/134409-900852.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_cac30bb317eb79a24a6b408d60ea662e%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-22%2F134409-900852.png&h=c5500be5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n*圖：dlwlrma@IG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n▼1預告中，IU 中性又充滿魅力的打扮，瞬間吸引了大眾的視線，以賭徒之姿充滿自信的掌握住全場氣氛，最後以犀利的眼神與壞笑結尾，十分霸氣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lUPJ8QFUUl0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DlUPJ8QFUUl0&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=9a203425\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lUPJ8QFUUl0</a><br />\n<br />\n此次第五張正規專輯〈LILAC〉中，《Celebrity》以獲得了熱烈迴響，另一首主打歌《LILAC》的預告▼2，則是展現了一刀未剪的武打場面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z90qbcmpwmQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dz90qbcmpwmQ&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=15807e4f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z90qbcmpwmQ</a><br />\n<br />\n▼3收錄曲《Flu》展現終極病態美。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YjdWNVSaUT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DYjdWNVSaUT8&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=756d9541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YjdWNVSaUT8</a><br />\n<br />\n▼4收錄曲《Epilogue》則是迷幻又神秘。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J1Zclb4Z4nk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJ1Zclb4Z4nk&d=VfnGJYDpQhHIir2SHpwXXB6eP3a%2FjAUraAi1lUB%2B7iI%3D&h=826520af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J1Zclb4Z4nk</a><br />\n<br />\n這次回歸的豐富程度，真的是難以想像啊！新專輯〈LILAC〉3月25日將正式發行，18:00公開新歌MV。<br />\n<br />\n*封面圖：1theK (원더케이)@youtube"},{"pid":"fdac5ad970a329bc8a71bc9f2be31b6c7f365806","tid":2457171,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:11:58.000Z","msg":"正..！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23b37b54154805be2fb60d6cbafa86851aa54b74","tid":2457171,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c1dd1f4d5c969bd24842ce5b8ce3576ab0537f","tid":2457171,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:50:49.000Z","msg":"會唔會太型<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b08a335cf4dd16f5e106953305a47d41e6f70096","tid":2457171,"uid":191107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"今晚又可以同老婆大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e42a8760304765a03cf54bde822b0a475d3b312","tid":2457171,"uid":56649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T13:52:05.000Z","msg":"allin<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9318c752783554d63557617ddab8815d4cbf8f","tid":2457171,"uid":275161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T14:06:40.000Z","msg":"當年等modern times嗰種期待到依家都冇變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}